{"tid":1480102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"路透社：美國商務部再延長華為臨時許可90日","createTime":"2019-08-17T07:15:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T01:42:04.000Z","uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fe047e330cad852c61fbdc43a2d8255307714ec6","tid":1480102,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:15:49.000Z","msg":"（中央社華盛頓16日綜合外電報導）路透社今天引述多名消息人士指出，美國商務部將延長華為的臨時許可證效期，讓華為在原先到期日19日後，能繼續購買美國產品，維持營運並提供顧客服務。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士透露，美方5月發給華為的臨時許可證，效期將延長90天。寬限期延長後，華為便可維持現有的電信網絡，也能繼續為目前華為裝置提供軟體更新。<br />\n<br />\n但由於華為的案子，已變成美國川普政府在美中貿易戰中重要的談判籌碼，消息人士提醒，目前情況仍然多變，延長寬限期的決定也可能在19日到期日前變卦。其中一名消息人士也透露，川普與習近平預計在這個週末通話，討論有關華為的事。<br />\n<br />\n身為全球最大電信設備製造商的華為，目前在沒有額外許可核准下，仍被川普政府禁止向美國企業購買元件生產新裝置。<br />\n<br />\n美國政府據稱，華為從事的活動違反美國國家安全或外交政策利益，因此將華為列入黑名單。川普政府也指控，華為的手機與網路設備能被北京用來監視美國人民，但華為多次否認。<br />\n<br />\n今天稍晚被問及華為臨時許可證一事時，美國商務部（U.S. Department of Commerce）不願評論，只請記者參考美國商務部長羅斯（Wilbur Ross）近日接受財經媒體CNBC專訪時的發言。<br />\n<br />\n羅斯在專訪中表示，臨時許可證效期只到19日，至於是否可能延長寬限期，他只說：「週一（19日）時我會很願意告訴大家最新狀況。」"},{"pid":"a0f35c76132f85d674db134608ed0801300cbc1d","tid":1480102,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a82df613c84ed4b30b7afb27068c9f1418647c","tid":1480102,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"371efee03101184b5277e280d904311b1d7ec1fc","tid":1480102,"uid":109923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:01:46.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c7cb49ff4dda90182383864083b9e2988b752be","tid":1480102,"uid":148438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:03:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be44923fa27042a1f3577db3e52ae6c3171c4b5","tid":1480102,"uid":56323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:06:15.000Z","msg":"都未確實延期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 19 號先知喎"},{"pid":"3a0cd87759433e06bc10c350f13fa9554573c9c9","tid":1480102,"uid":132189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:18:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌"},{"pid":"a59f165e1b2eaa8638a17de0cf35da9c8e649d3b","tid":1480102,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:20:01.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借一借位～<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>保護自己資產，全民唱美元現鈔！</strong></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1478882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1478882</a>"},{"pid":"3a68471dd9f24ff65e1e92b1ea84eef358cf3e3f","tid":1480102,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:41:15.000Z","msg":"一日都唔多得"},{"pid":"87d792a62646f2d63649d338242ea77b06137ed4","tid":1480102,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又廷"},{"pid":"04eb6486f6ffe4457393276186b99297472c038f","tid":1480102,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:20:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/21/30/10213078_576972.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F21%2F30%2F10213078_576972.jpg&h=ee06d3f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190716/_2019071622285880249.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%